Madame!

1546
01:54:43,812 --> 01:54:45,313
Maestro!

1547
01:55:04,166 --> 01:55:05,583
Lumière!

1548
01:55:06,793 --> 01:55:09,086
Relógio, vencemos o relógio!

1549
01:55:14,176 --> 01:55:15,176
Plumette!

1550
01:55:16,094 --> 01:55:18,095
Plumette!

1551
01:55:44,414 --> 01:55:46,415
Chip! Olha para ti!

1552
01:55:47,250 --> 01:55:48,668
Voltaste a ser um menino!

1553
01:55:48,835 --> 01:55:50,878
